        <abstract> 
<p>A big book arrived for GHD before CD left Down. Hopes it is Thomson and Tait [<hi rend="italic">Treatise on natural philosophy</hi>, 2 vols., 2d ed. (1869)]. It shows what they think of GHD.</p> 
            <p>Thinks it grand if GHD has made a correction about "such an old sinner as the Sun" and hopes his arithmetic on his old subject will turn out right.</p>
        </abstract>
